Interface Evaluator<P>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of the phenotype that is evaluated
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DTLZ1, DTLZ2, DTLZ3, DTLZ4, DTLZ5, DTLZ6, DTLZ7, HelloWorldEvaluator, KnapsackOverloadEvaluator, KnapsackProfitEvaluator, LOTZEvaluator, MinOnesEvaluator, MultiEvaluator, QueensErrorEvaluator, QueensEvaluator, SalesmanEvaluator, WFG1, WFG2, WFG3, WFG4, WFG5, WFG6, WFG7, WFG8, WFG9, WFGEvaluator, WFGI1, WFGI2, WFGI3, WFGI4, WFGI5, ZDT1, ZDT2, ZDT3, ZDT4, ZDT5, ZDT6

    public interface Evaluator<P>
    The Evaluator evaluates phenotypes to Objectives. The Evaluator must always add the same Objectives to the Objectives.
    See Also:
